    penaltyForAbsence: "EDD: back payroll taxes plus 10-15% penalties plus interest. Labor Commissioner: back wages, overtime, benefits, and liquidated damages for all misclassified workers. Criminal penalties under Labor Code §226.8: $5,000-$25,000 per violation. Attorney General enforcement actions.",
